title: Standardize/optimize redirection
type: issue
--- 
Many env methods tail the werror using:

  router.capture('werror') do |device|

Surely there is a faster way to do this... to say hook up an array buffer that receives werror by default.  Unless otherwise specified werror will go there, eliminating the need to setup a temporary StringIO.